<![CDATA[<div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: right;"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif; "><font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000066" size="6">{!Contact.SchoolText__c}</font></span></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: right;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="'Times New Roman', Times, serif" color="#ff6600" size="4"><i>Chartered By The British Schools Foundation</i></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: right;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif" color="#c0c0c0" size="6"><b><i><br></i></b></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: right;"><font style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div style="text-align: left;"><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="4"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="border-spacing: 5px;">Dear&nbsp;{!Contact.Salutation} {!Contact.LastName},</span></font></div><div><span class="Apple-style-span" style="border-spacing: 5px;"><div><div><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 12.8px;">&nbsp;</span></div><div><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial;"><span style="white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">After four very busy and enjoyable years in KL, Alison and I have decided that this will be our last academic year at BSKL.</span></div><div><span id="docs-internal-guid-d8f1a51a-bce9-d775-5ee7-90866f024006"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-right: -0.75pt;"><span style="vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">We left the UK four years ago to have an international experience and we have found our time here at BSKL fabulously enriching. Professionally and personally we are now ready for our next adventure.</span></p><br><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-right: -0.75pt;"><span style="vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">It will not be easy for us to leave such an excellent school. &nbsp;So much has been achieved during our time here. The primary school has gone from strength to strength, and a growing middle school has developed into one of the leading secondary schools in the Asian region. Both Alison and I are immensely proud of what has been achieved at BSKL since we arrived.</span></p><br><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-right: -0.75pt;"><span style="vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Mrs Brock and the Board have already begun a thorough and exhaustive selection process to appoint a new Head of Secondary who will take over from me next summer. An appointment will likely be made before the end of this term, leaving plenty of time for a smooth transition. In the same way that I was able to meet many of you before I actually joined the school, parents will have the opportunity to meet the new Head of Secondary before the start of next academic year. Given the strength of the school, I have no doubt the post will attract many outstanding candidates and BSKL will be spoilt for choice.</span></p><br><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-right: -0.75pt;"><span style="vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Alison and I have both been privileged to work with a talented and committed staff, and alongside parents, to play a role in the education of an amazing group of pupils. We look forward to continuing to work with you all during the course of this year and as always we are very grateful for your continued support.</span></p><br><p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-right: -0.75pt;"><span style="vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Kind regards</span></p><br><span style="vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Derek Mackey
Head of Secondary </span></font></span></div></div></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div></span></div></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: left;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif">{!Contact.SchoolText__c}</font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: left;"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><i><font class="Apple-style-span" color="#ff6600"><b>World Class Education</b></font></i></span></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: left;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: left;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif">__________________________________________________________</font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: center;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="1">{!User.School_List_Email_Footer__c}</font><font class="Apple-style-span" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="1">&nbsp;</font></div>]]></td>
